cs.DL, cs.EE, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY 

The paper discusses the efficiency of research in the EU, particularly in the field of technological research. This could fall under several sub-categories in computer science, including digital libraries (cs.DL) for analyzing citation data, electrical engineering (cs.EE) for studying technological advancements, information retrieval (cs.IR) for analyzing research trends, social and information networks (cs.SI) for studying the distribution of papers, and cybersecurity (cs.CY) for discussing the risks to Europeans' future.
